QuestData.Title: WANTED: Spineslicer's Husk
QuestData.Description: Posted by: Quartermaster Jolie$B$BWe're running out of supplies to repair our troops' armor.$B$BI'll pay handsomely for the husk of the mighty ravager Spineslicer. It would provide us with repair materials for weeks.
QuestData.CompletionText: Oh, commander! What an honor!$B$BHow can I help you?
QuestData.RewardText: I didn't think anyone could actually kill the beast. Thank you, commander!
